	<a name=Prikazy></a><h1>Prikazy</h1>
	<p>
		<h2>Automaticke zarovnanie textu na spodok strany</h2>
		<p>
		\vspace*{\fill}
		</p>
		<h2>Vkladanie PDF do texu</h2>
		<p>
		\usepackage{pdfpages}<br><br>
		\includepdf[landscape=false]{./subor1.pdf}<br>
		\includepdf[pages=1]{./subor2.pdf}<br>
		\includepdf[pages=2]{./subor2.pdf}<br>
		</p>
		<h2>Cislovanie tabuliek, obrazkov, vzorcov</h2>
		<p>
		\usepackage{chngcntr} &nbsp&nbsp <b>% - balicek ktory nastavuje cislovania objektov </b><br>
		\counterwithin{objekt}{typ_urovne} &nbsp&nbsp <b>% - zmeni cislovania objektu podla typu_urovne (section, chapter, subsection, susussubsection ...) </b>Priklad prvy obrazok v sekcii 3 bude mat cislo 31<br>
		\renewcommand{\theOBJEKT}{\arabic{typ_urovne}.\arabic{objekt}} <b>% &nbsp&nbsp - ovlyvnuje nastavenie cize v tomto pripade prida bodku medzi cilo urovne a cislo obketu.</b> Priklad prvy obrazok v sekcii 3 bude mat cislo 3.1<br>
		</p>
		<h3>Zmena cislovania obrazkov</h3>
		<p>
		\usepackage{chngcntr}   <br><br>
		%\counterwithout{figure}{section} &nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp <b>- neviem naco je zatial</b><br>
		\counterwithin{figure}{section}<br>
		\renewcommand{\thefigure}{\arabic{section}.\arabic{figure}}<br>
		</p>
		<h3>Zmena cislovania rovnic</h3>
		<p>
		\usepackage{chngcntr} <br><br>
		\counterwithin{equation}{section}<br>
		\renewcommand{\theequation}{\arabic{section}.\arabic{equation}}
		</p>
		<h3>Zmena cislovania Tabuliek</h3>
		<p>
		\usepackage{chngcntr} <br><br>
		\counterwithin{table}{section}<br>
		\renewcommand{\thetable}{\arabic{section}.\arabic{table}}
		</p>
	

	</p>
	<h1>Potrebne balicky podla marie (zatial som nepotreboval)</h1>
	<p>
kniznice co treba doinstalovat do texu:</br></br>
texlive-generic-extra</br>
texlive-math-extra</br>
texlive-plain-extra</br>
texlive-latex-extra</br>
texlive-fonts-extra</br>
texlive-lang-czechslovak</br>
texlive-bibtex-extra</br>
texlive-science</br>

	</p>
	
